<header>
<div id="instruction">
Here are some extracts from letters from people explaining why they were unable to attend a meeting. Complete them by filling each gap with the past simple of the verb given in brackets. You will need to use both active and passive voice.
</div>
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/gt_set7.1_04.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  
  <ol id="questionList">
  <li>My daughter&#xA0; <input id="q1"/> &#xA0;(fall) off a chair at school,&#xA0; <input id="q2"/> &#xA0;(hit) her head and&#xA0; <input id="q3"/> &#xA0;(take) to hospital.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>My dog&#xA0; <input id="q4"/> &#xA0;(involve) in a fight with another dog and I&#xA0; <input id="q5"/> &#xA0;(have) to pull them apart. The other dog then&#xA0; <input id="q6"/> &#xA0;(attack) me and I&#xA0; <input id="q7"/> &#xA0;(bit) extremely badly and&#xA0; <input id="q8"/> &#xA0;(have) to go to hospital.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>The lift&#xA0; <input id="q9"/> &#xA0;(break down) and I&#xA0; <input id="q10"/> &#xA0;(trap) for over an hour. I&#xA0; <input id="q11"/> &#xA0;(not have) my mobile phone with me so I&#xA0; <input id="q12"/> &#xA0;(have) to wait for the emergency services to rescue me.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>I&#xA0; <input id="q13"/> &#xA0;(run) over a stone on my bicycle,&#xA0; <input id="q14"/> &#xA0;(go) flying over the handlebars and&#xA0; <input id="q15"/> &#xA0;(knock) unconscious.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>I&#xA0; <input id="q16"/> &#xA0;(give) hepatitis vaccination for my holiday and I&#xA0; <input id="q17"/> &#xA0;(develop) a high fever and&#xA0; <input id="q18"/> &#xA0;(feel) extremely nauseous.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>My five-year-old son&#xA0; <input id="q19"/> &#xA0;(catch) chicken pox. He was running a fever and&#xA0; <input id="q20"/> &#xA0;(come) out in a nasty skin rash so I&#xA0; <input id="q21"/> &#xA0;(stay) at home to look after him.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>I&#xA0; <input id="q22"/> &#xA0;(undergo) a minor operation last week but there&#xA0; <input id="q23"/> &#xA0;(be) complications and I&#xA0; <input id="q24"/> &#xA0;(not discharge) from hospital until yesterday.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>I&#xA0; <input id="q25"/> &#xA0;(trip) over one of my children's toys and&#xA0; <input id="q26"/> &#xA0;(sprain) my ankle. I&#xA0; <input id="q27"/> &#xA0;(tell) by the doctor not to walk for three days.</li>
  
  <p class="linespace"></p>
  <li>My wife and I&#xA0; <input id="q28"/> &#xA0;(involve) in a minor car accident. We&#xA0; <input id="q29"/> &#xA0;(not injure) but our car&#xA0; <input id="q30"/> &#xA0;(damage) in the collision.</li>
  <p class="linespace"></p>
</ol>
